## Architecture & Code Quality
- Use named exports always.

## Design Principles
- Must follow single responsibility principal.
- Must follow DRY.

## Documentation
- Must include IDE IntelliSense-friendly comments and descriptions for each component, hook, and function.

## Testing
- Must have 100% test coverage.
- Test case descriptions must start with a capital letter.

## Naming
- Use dash-case names for files.
